comments: Jokic (DEN) makes marginal contact with Paschall (GSW) that doesn't affect his SQBR during his drive.
Jokic (DEN) makes clean contact with the ball prior to making incidental contact with Paschall's (GSW) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Porter Jr. (DEN) makes clean contact with the ball after the shot was blocked by Jokic (DEN).
Correctly called 24 Second Violation.
Plumlee (DEN) and Green (GSW) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound.
Lee (GSW) delivers contact to Porter Jr.'s (DEN) body during his shot attempt near the rim.
Beasley (DEN) makes clean contact with the ball during Russell's (GSW) drive. Any additional contact to Russell's leg is incidental.
Russell (GSW) makes contact to Jokic's (DEN) head/neck area.
Cauley-Stein (GSW) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Barton's (DEN) path and he absorbs the oncoming contact during the screen.
Burks (GSW) cleanly dislodges the ball from Plumlee (DEN) during the rebound.
Jokic (DEN) turns and delivers contact to Burks' (GSW) body during his driving shot attempt.
Burks (GSW) and Plumlee (DEN) briefly engage in marginal contact off ball prior to separating.
Green (GSW) is in the paint and actively guarding an opponent within three seconds.
Barton (DEN) gathers the ball and proceeds to take three steps.
Porter Jr. (DEN) cleanly dislodges the ball during Lee's (GSW) driving shot attempt.
Beasley (DEN) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Green's (GSW) path and he is firming up when the contact occurs during the screen.
Green (GSW) makes marginal contact to Jokic's (DEN) off-arm and body after his release and doesn't affect his shot attempt.
Porter Jr. (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position during Burks' (GSW) jump shot attempt.
Jokic's (DEN) arm collapses to his body and he absorbs the oncoming contact with Burks (GSW) when the two players come together during the drive. Burks changes direction and continues his drive.
Jokic (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position during Burks' (GSW) shot attempt.
Green (GSW) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Porter Jr. (DEN) removes his hand from the ball and he slightly extends his arm into Green's (GSW) arm during the driving shot attempt. The contact is marginal.
Barton (DEN) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Russell (GSW) after the release of the ball during his jump shot attempt.
Plumlee (DEN) initiates foot to foot contact with Russell (GSW) during the drive. Russell (GSW) moves through the contact and continues his drive.

Porter Jr.'s (DEN) right arm collapses to his body and he absorbs the body contact with Burks (GSW) when the two players come together while moving in the same direction. Porter Jr.'s (DEN) left elbow makes contact with the ball.
Burks (GSW) makes hand on ball contact with Barton (DEN) as he attempts to receive the hand off from Jokic (DEN). The contact is incidental.
Beasley (DEN) does not dislodge Russell (GSW) from his legal guarding position. Russell's (GSW) reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Spellman (GSW) makes marginal contact with Beasley's (DEN) arm and doesn't affect his ability to pass.
Lee (GSW) jumps from point A to point B and delivers contact to Porter Jr.'s (DEN) body that affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Beasley (DEN) makes contact to Burks' (GSW) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Green (GSW) commits a take foul on Beasley (DEN).
Russell (GSW) commits a take foul on Plumlee (DEN).
Green (GSW) and Jokic (DEN) enters the paint prior to the release of the ball during Plumlee's (DEN) free throw attempt.
Green (GSW) holds Jokic's (DEN) shorts and makes contact to his arm during the rebound. The contact affects Jokic's FOM.
Lee (GSW) commits a take foul on Beasley (DEN).
